rows.label: qev087403_MSG0001
rows.name: He's got to be around here somewhere...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0002
rows.name: Ooh, Elma! There he is![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0003
rows.name: Mustache-spotting is fun![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0004
rows.name: Let's see what he's up to.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0005
rows.name: Looks like work. ...For once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0006
rows.name: Maintenance is falling behind, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0007
rows.name: Makes sense. Combat got a little rough 'n tumble yesterday.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0008
rows.name: Let's start with the units that took the most damage.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0009
rows.name:
It'll be quicker to strip 'em down for spare parts
than spending weeks fixin' 'em up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0010
rows.name: Sounds good, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0011
rows.name:
We can use the electronics and generators as is,
but the secondary armor's shot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0012
rows.name: All right then, we'll need new materials to patch it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0013
rows.name: Hey! You rubberneckers busy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0014
rows.name: Rubberneckers?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0015
rows.name:
That's a bit unfair,
seeing as how you ordered us to watch you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0016
rows.name:
Ah, you know what I meant.
Anyway, you'd be helping out BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0017
rows.name:
The sightseein' tour is over for nowâ€”
see if you can scrounge up what we need, all right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0018
rows.name: Lazy mustache man should do it himself![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0019
rows.name:
No can do, potato cake.
Gotta stay here and oversee the mechanics.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0020
rows.name: Now off with ya.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev087403_MSG0021
rows.name: I guess a mission's a mission...[ST:wait ]
